headline: How Target’s (TGT) Exclusive Holiday Partnerships Could Reshape Its Competitive Edge
summary: In early October 2025, Target announced the rollout of multiple exclusive product collections and immersive in-store experiences with major partners like Universal Pictures, Netflix, FlavCity, and TRUBAR, all hitting stores and online in the critical lead-up to the holiday shopping season.
